if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da9bccb98bc83f1022b733dfbfb2e9af0d3ccef","tid":1715634,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QOgd1WE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQOgd1WE.jpg&h=39ffb3a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a0b9fb34b28118621c3a1dd2e09fc13325fa9a8","tid":1715634,"uid":75353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:22:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9887b751db7726b447c131a3e26526d107d624c","tid":1715634,"uid":116645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:25:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a70e3320de8fcf247881bba26781acd514b3fabe","tid":1715634,"uid":316048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:27:18.000Z","msg":"設獨立調查委員會 還看北京 (轉載節錄)<br />\n過去這個夏天，不少香港人流汗、流淚甚至流血，成千上萬群眾在街頭吶喊過無數次，高呼「五大訴求 缺一不可」，要求政府回應。五大訴求中，由於當局已經撤回《逃犯條例》修訂，若說設獨立調查委員會（COI）是港人訴求的最大公因數，相信無人會反對。儘管連月來民意非常清晰，但港府高層繼續置若罔聞或稱「不是此時」.....<br />\n<br />\n以下係小弟發夢幻想有一個城市個失去警察公信力既情況:<br />\n<br />\n如果市民認為警察公信力盡失，由警方做任何「獨立」監管或調查都未必能令社會平息暴力。但政府遲遲不做只係因為怕警隊出現反抗...而反抗後果係:<br />\n<br />\n1. 警察大罷工，然後市面上會「突然」出現非常多的罪案，犯罪者是誰 ? 大家可以思考下，而令社會「回復」和平的代價就係取消獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n2. 警察持槍大遊行，你懂的<br />\n<br />\n可否用軍方力量整冶? 我認為認為係可以<br />\n客觀分析，其實未必冇可能，國家領導層能一石二鳥，一可以化解民怨，二可建立一個訊息比大家知，就係只係一直都只係警察前線胡作非為冇聽上頭指示，不失為得民心之方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於軍方力量點清算，可以有2個方法:<br />\n1. 混入前線 (包括滲透內部相同意見人仕)，係執行職務時搜集證據，交由獨立委員會清算<br />\n2. 係前線下班後用武力拘捕"},{"pid":"890ed04622209a2f55a07841669481d3e93b9b72","tid":1715634,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98c42e5bc085e1392608b87363b532009ceb3f5","tid":1715634,"uid":51540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:30:21.000Z","msg":"一日冇主權就唔會有民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01336cce1fa0a34b0454e594b3811494a0b37d32","tid":1715634,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:32:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"859d14a2145fddc8c900bcd9b1699a4f81f4bd00","tid":1715634,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:38:36.000Z","msg":"嗱！依家機會就俾咗你中共<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立呢條路用唔用就睇你港共選擇。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求/香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n二揀一<br />\n<br />\n一旦落實就不惜一切代價去搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdaf7bc0fd01e22b522465aa34f4c23a6a9e27f4","tid":1715634,"uid":36543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cd94ca2edd144460a62d02f34f337fda5546e29","tid":1715634,"uid":258598,"like":20,"dislike":87,"score":-67,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:39:07.000Z","msg":"林鄭真人上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ce0c263846783b9cf823de60c147d94cbe6ee8","tid":1715634,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:39:34.000Z","msg":"要用死線逼政府<br />\n<br />\n三罷再拖對我哋都不利"},{"pid":"461c5badd88b2dd2e5c9404120cdbd3f5447f087","tid":